transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

If you're looking to whiten your teeth, then these guys should be your best friends. Today I'm going to show you how to use Crest White strips to whiten you're teeth. Peel the upper strip from the backing liner and align with the gum line of you're top teeth so you're teeth are completely covered by the gel side of your strip but without overlapping your gums. Press gently for good contact. Fold the rest of your strip behind your teeth to keep in place. Repeat the same for your bottom set of teeth. Leave on for 30 minutes, remove, and throw away.
